  "title": "Speed Paths",
  "description": "Allows you to obtain the speed effect when walking on path blocks [1.21.2 - 26.1.x]",
  "body": "<div align=\"center\">\n  <h1>Speed Paths</h1>\n  <br/>\n  <p>\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Release-3.0.x-limegreen\" alt=\"Release\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Minecraft-1.21.2%2026.1.x-blue?logo=data:image/png;base64,&logoWidth=50\" alt=\"Minecraft\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/License-CC_BY_4.0-blueviolet\" alt=\"License CC BY 4.0\">\n    <a href=\"https://discord.gg/Tq83Zuhduv\" target=\"_blank\">\n      <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1358706268012810350?color=5865F2&label=Discord&logo=discord&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Discord\">\n    </a>\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/2KSlu1VD?logo=modrinth&label=Modrinth\" alt=\"Modrinth\">\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<br/>\n<br/>\n\n<h2>✨ Features</h2>\n<h3>🏃 Main description</h3>\n<blockquote>This lightweight datapack grants players a Speed effect when walking on dirt path blocks.<br/> Depending on the setup, the boost can range from Speed I to Speed V, making movement significantly faster on these paths.</blockquote>\n\n<h3>⚡ Use and benefits</h3>\n<blockquote>Perfect for creating fast travel routes in villages, bases, or between key locations, this system allows efficient movement without relying on complex mechanics like redstone or ice.<br/> A real time-saver.</blockquote>\n\n<h3>🧩 Gameplay integration</h3>\n<blockquote>The system is simple and intuitive: standing or walking on a path automatically activates the effect.<br/> It fits seamlessly into vanilla gameplay while encouraging the creation of practical and aesthetic road networks.</blockquote>\n\n<br/>\n\n<h2>💬 Commands</h2>\n<blockquote>\n  <code>/function speed_paths:set_<values></code> <i>values ​​range from 1 to 5</i> - Changes the speed level<br/><br/>\n  <code>/function speed_paths:menu_speed_path</code> - Opens the chat options menu<br/><br/>\n  <code>/function speed_paths:give_book</code> - Gives you the book with the options<br/><br/>\n  <code>/function speed_paths:disable</code> - Sets the speed to 0 <i>\"disables the datapack\"</i><br/><br/>\n  <code>/function speed_paths:enable</code> - Gives you the book with the options and opens the chat options menu<br/><br/>\n  <code>/function speed_paths:help</code> - In-game help command\n</blockquote>\n\n<br/>\n\n<h2>📥 Installation</h2>\n<h3>📁 Datapack</h3>\n<blockquote>\n  Drop the <code>.zip</code> file into your world's <code>datapacks</code> folder.<br/>\n  Reload the world or use <code>/reload</code>.<br/>\n  Enjoy your enchanted adventure!\n</blockquote>\n\n<h3>⚙️ Mod</h3>\n<blockquote>\n  Drop the <code>.jar</code> file into the <code>mods</code> folder of your instance.<br/>\n  <code>Restart</code> your game.<br/>\n  Have fun!\n</blockquote>",
